			UnixWare Hints+Tips
			-------------------

Introduction
------------

This section of the mail server is dedicated to various hints & tips
that we have found useful - we hope you do to!

If you find any problems with these, have a better way to solve the
problem or would like to make additions to this list then please email
"plord@novell.co.uk".


